**  MSG (ERROR MESSAGE )
E-01 INPUT MACHINE
E-02 INPUT ADMITTED DAY START
E-03 ADMITTED DAY START ISN'T RIGHT
E-04 INPUT START ADMITTED TIME
E-05 START ADMITTED TIME ISN'T RIGHT
E-06 INPUT ADMITTED DAY EXIT
E-07 EXIT ADMITTED TIME ISN'T RIGHT
E-08 INPUT EXIT ADMITTED TIME
E-09 EXIT ADMITTED TIME ISN'T RIGHT
E-10 ADMITTED DAY START IS BIGGER THAN EXIT DAY
E-11 START ADMITTED TIME IS BIGGER THAN EXIT TIME
E-12 THERE ISN'T APPLICABLE DATA.
